title: Hamilton HyperSync CAM 1080p
description: To kick off the New Year in style, a fresh encoding of the hit musical which syncs adinbied's original 1080p CAMrip with the Original Broadway Cast Recording. Though not without precedent, this version has been made with thousands of individual timing adjustments for syllable-perfect accuracy wherever possible. Other changes: Embedded [NOT hardcoded] English subtitles Embedded chapter markers for all songs Masked the DVDFab logo Entire show in one file There are text splashes at intro and intermission, and a brief credits sequence. All King George scenes are synced but use cam audio for reasons that are hopefully self-evident.
